    },
    {
      "type": "step",
      "number": "1",
      "text": "Using a Thickness Gauge, measure the axial girth at the large end of the connecting rod. Connecting rod large end axial misalignment Std. 0.2－0.4mm Limit value: 1 0.5mm"
    },
    {
      "type": "attention",
      "items": [
        "If the limit value is exceeded, replace the connecting rod and re-inspect. If the limit value is still exceeded at the re-inspection, replace the crankshaft."
